title: For What (Intro)
lyrics:
What’s the meaning of all of this?
What the fuck?
My hair looks terrible
Did I turn the stove off?
I feel so awkward
Terrible

Why is this nigga texting me?

Man, I’m tired

I hate the way this looks

I feel weird

I don’t know anymore

What time is it?

I wanna give up

Why is this shit taking so long?

I’m going to call him right back

Lucky I called him yesterday

Damn, did I feed the cat?

Have we been waiting this whole time?

For what?
